latestIgtvVideos.title: How to get that Chic Factor💄
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In this video I have mentioned few ways to instantly enhance your basic look and get a classy, chic factor

1.Tuck in or tie a knot to create a classy look 💃
2. Add a belt to create a statement 🙌
3. Accessorizing is must, so you can add any of your favourite accessory 💍
4. Use a handbag, here you can also go for poppy colours 👛
5. Add hair accessories like hairs clips, hair bands 👒
6. Go for layering, using shrugs, blazers , jackets etc.🧥
7. Wear a Red lipstick whenever you have a doubt 💄
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dressing according to Footwear 🖤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Footwear plays a very important role when it comes to styling or dressing up for any occasion, so in this video I have tried to dress as per my footwear 😉

1. For transparent heels, I have selected a fit & flare dress
Heels: @shein_in 

2. For brown slingback flats, I have selected a formal look, pairing a white trouser with tank top and blazer to complete the look
Flats: @streetstylestoreofficial 

3. For black flats, I have combined a black palazzo with white shirt and black sunglasses
Flats : @streetstylestoreofficial 

4. When it comes to white sneakers, we have unlimited options and here I have paired it with a simple jumpsuit

5. For black boots, I have paired a turtle neck pullover with blue jeans and added black high knee socks to just enhance the whole look

latestIgtvVideos.title: 3 easy ways of styling flare pants❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Being a true believer of buying less, choosing well and making it last - I love mixing & matching clothes to create a new look each time

In this video, I have used my grandpa's flared trouser to create 3 simple looks

1. Paired the trouser with one shoulder top and added accessories, this is a super cool bruch look 🍜

2. Paired the trouser with tank top, added sneakers & watch. This look is great for shopping or hanging out with friends 👜

3. Paired the trouser with Red Polka Dot crop top, added white sandals. Here, you can add a hat or Sunglasses to get a perfect beach or outing look👒

latestPosts.caption:
A little love letter to old-school charm and effortless ethnic style✨

Kurtas & white pants @astarqala 

A pastel pink kurta adorned with white chikankari: soft & sweet. Paired with denim and dainty heels, this look is a gentle nod to those afternoon chai moments and innocent smiles. The kind of outfit that makes you want to twirl under the sun or hum an old Lata Mangeshkar tune.Perfect for brunch dates, casual festivities, or a cozy day out with loved ones 🌸

Then comes the bold, festive side, a lime green kurta with classic embroidery, paired with breezy white palazzos and old-school footwear. A look that says “I’m here, I shine, but always with grace.” Add a vintage clutch and chandbaalis, and you’re ready to steal the spotlight, just like the heroine in a timeless film. Perfect for mehendi functions, family gatherings, or a festive day at work 🍀

Brunch plans, but not without my go-to skincare ritual✨

This @pondsindia Detan Face Wash with Niacinamide & Vitamin C fades tan and brings my glow back in just 7 days💛

Skin is fresh, mood is set… went with a soft glam modern vibe today! 💅 When skincare & style team up, it’s always a win 🥂
